      "writtenOn": "2018-06-08T23:47:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I feel like this is overbuilt, and introduces potential for errors.  There\u0027s really only two practical choices anyways, 302 (temporary) and 301 (cacheable).  Consider making the API surface smaller by changing this to a \"Permanent bool\" (or \"Cacheable bool\")",
      "revId": "fcba2f921d28caf0bc5c4a342ae96cd463996b98",
