      "writtenOn": "2018-06-09T00:00:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i am following existing API: https://godoc.org/net/http#Redirect\nmaking this bool or having a separate enum for accepted values of status here would be an extra generalization, but I am not sure about its value *shrug*",
